                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/1838.</note>
                <head>[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-05-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 18, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>At 11 o’clock last night the armistice between the Government and the
                    revolutionists went into effect.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
